features: Small & Powerful: With 25W charging power but smaller size, this charger is more convenient and portable. It only takes 30min to charge your Samsung Galaxy S24/S23 ultra from 0 to 60%, 5 times as fast as standard USB C charger.

10FT C Charger Cable Fast Charging: The 25W super fast type c charger is equipped with extra longer 10FT USB C fast charger cable, offering a user-friendly reversible design and longer charging distance, fast charging and up to 480 Mbps data transfer speed. The power output up to 3 Amp and 100-240 volt input of this 2pack Samsung super fast chargers can charge two devices simultaneously, ideal for worldwide travel with your partner!

Safety Assurance: The Samsung galaxy S24 S23 ultra super fast charger is built in intelligent chips, which can protect your devices against damage caused by short circuit, over-current, over-voltage, over-heating, and over-charging issues. Automatically stops charging when battery capacity is full to ensure your device safety and longevity.

Super Fast Charger Universal Compatibility: The Samsung fast charger supports most of USB C devices, including Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra/S24/S24+/S23 Ultra/S23/S23+/S21/ S21+/ S21 Ultra 5G/ S22/S22+/S22 Ultra/Note10/ 10+, Note 20/20 Ultra 5G, S20/S20+/S20 Ultra 5G/ S20 FE(Fan Edition) 5G, S10, S10+, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best charger I have ever owned.
reviews.reviewText: I can't recommend the Super Fast Charger Type C enough. As a user with both the S23 and S21 Ultra, these chargers work like a charm, providing speedy and efficient charging. The 10FT C Charger Cable is a game-changer, offering a generous length that adds convenience to charging in various settings.What sets these chargers apart is their durability. In a world where chargers often wear out quickly, these have proven to be exceptionally robust. They're now my go-to chargers, and I haven't experienced any issues with their performance.Charging from 0 to 60% in just 30 minutes is a game-changer, especially when I'm on the go.If you're tired of constantly replacing chargers and want a reliable, fast-charging solution, these Super Fast Chargers Type C are the way to go.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Remember this is designed for use with Samsung phones!
reviews.reviewText: The product comes with two, so I gave the other to my spouse.She uses a Motorola phone, it charges but not as quick. Much like a regular charger.On my Samsung, when you insert cord one way it says "Super Fast Charger" when you insert the opposite way, it charges like a regular slow charger. You could use a sharpie and put a dot on the fast side but I had a pack of cheap small jewels with adhesive on one side and this worked perfect for me.By the way, I was concerned about the extra long cords but after receiving them, the length to me was a plus because with two people charging in the same room, I can use a different outlet altogether and not be intrusive to the other person's needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best charger yet
reviews.reviewText: I've bought this item (2 pack with 10 ft cables) 3 times now. Not because they've gone bad, but because I've had one stolen, and I wanted backups. Then I also decided to put one in the office and one in the bedroom. I have nothing bad to say about them. They've all worked flawlessly and have never gone bad, and still charge at a super-fast speed. The oldest one I have is about 13 months old I think and works just as well as the one I bought a week ago. My ONLY complaint (if you could call it that) is that I'm more a fan of the feel of braided cables instead of the rubber ones, but for THIS type of cable, I give it 10/10 Would (and probably will) buy again!
